Project: Apna.co Job Details Page Clone 
 
Project Overview 
Develop a pixel-perfect clone of the Apna.co Job Details page by replicating the design, layout, 
responsiveness, navigation flow, and user interface components as closely as possible. 
The cloned application should provide the same user experience as the original website, 
including job information display, company details, application sections, job highlights, related 
jobs, and responsive behavior across different screen sizes. 
Reference URLs:  Apna Job Listing 1     Apna Job Listing 2 
Requirements 
Functional Requirements 
• Replicate the complete UI design.  
• Create reusable React components.  
• Implement responsive layouts for:  
o Desktop  
o Tablet  
o Mobile  
• Dynamic job details rendering using mock JSON data.  
• Navigation between multiple job pages.  
• Similar typography, spacing, cards, buttons, and sections.  
• Sticky Apply Button.  
• Similar footer and header sections.  
• Related Jobs Section.  
• Company Information Section. 

 
